NAME
    EBook::EPUB::Valid - perl wrapper for EpubCheck

SYNOPSIS
      use EBook::EPUB::Valid;
      my ($is_valid, $out) = validate_epub('/path/to/file.epub');

  Command Line Interface
      epubcheck [epubcheck-x.x.x.jar] file.epub

DESCRIPTION
    EBook::EPUB::Valid is a perl wrapper for EpubCheck. EpubCheck is a tool
    to validate IDPF EPUB files.

SUBROUTINES
  ($is_valid, $out) = validate_epub( [ $path_to_epubcheck_jar ], $path_to_epub_file )
    Validates $path_to_epub_file by using $path_to_epubcheck_jar. If
    $path_to_epubcheck_jar is omitted, bundled 'epubcheck-3.0.1.jar' is
    used.

AUTHOR
    pawa <pawapawa@cpan.org>

